#include .gitignore

**venv**

# Ansys Fluent / CFD
*.trn
cleanup-fluent-*.bat
FM_*
fluent-*-error.log
fluent-*.log
.venv_gui/
.venv/

# ── Distributed Lock Orchestration ──────────────────────────────────
# The sync_locks/ directory MUST be synced across all lab computers.
# It contains .lock and .done marker files used by the Wait-and-See
# Leader Election protocol (see StellarOrionEngineMach5Up.py).
# Without this, multi-computer orchestration will break.
#
# The opt_checkpoint.json must also sync so a second computer can
# load the full sample matrix and training data when joining a run.
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
!sync_locks/
!CADDesign/opt_checkpoint.json
